    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塗鴉之城曾是一個匯聚音樂、潮流與創造活力的繁華中心，如今卻淪為一片充斥著豪華公寓、企業高樓與死寂街道的冰冷地帶。公共藝術被明令禁止，音樂演出許可無從獲取。市民們在沉寂乏味中虛度光陰。<br><br>但從破碎的街道縫隙中，新的浪潮正悄然崛起。<br><br>舞者、樂手和塗鴉藝術家們組成團隊，重回街頭，形成了名為「火花輪滑」的地下聯盟，為了地盤、為了表達、為了變革而戰。你的團隊是最新的挑戰者：規模雖小，但鬥志昂揚，潛力無窮。<br><br>提升排名，贏得粉絲，點燃一場變革運動。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/9aac487fce6063db8f5955695d945bc5.poster.avif?t=1770155301\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/9aac487fce6063db8f5955695d945bc5.webm?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/9aac487fce6063db8f5955695d945bc5.mp4?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>以風格制霸街頭的戰術</strong><br>移动不止是改变位置，更是炫技表演。利用城市中的滑轨、坡道与垂直地形，在每次转弯时串联组合各类特技。赚取的风格值还能用于释放最强的技能。 <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/493ba6fe7914c748f3384974fe4000f4.poster.avif?t=1770155301\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/493ba6fe7914c748f3384974fe4000f4.webm?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/493ba6fe7914c748f3384974fe4000f4.mp4?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>佔領地圖，扭轉戰局</strong> <br>散佈在各關卡中的標記點不僅僅是裝飾——它們是戰略目標。佔領標記點作為你的地盤，併為團隊生成風格值，但務必準備好保衛你的標記，防止敵對幫派將你名字從城市牆上抹去。 <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/0230166a6fa3e820dbd2c008e10ad62d.poster.avif?t=1770155301\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/0230166a6fa3e820dbd2c008e10ad62d.webm?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/0230166a6fa3e820dbd2c008e10ad62d.mp4?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>迎戰各路對手</strong> <br>每個街區都被懷有不同目的的幫派所佔據——從企業贊助的精英小隊，到渴求名望的網紅團體，乃至混亂不羈的行為藝術者。智勝他們的戰術，贏得觀眾們的尊重。 <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/4cb6033986a8fa5bcf65bb81c73e2b09.poster.avif?t=1770155301\" aria-label=\"Shows Hop jumping in the air to perform a dance attack, shows Star doing an attack on her bass guitar and effecting two enemy Taggers, shows Hop perform a dance move that damages three enemies\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/4cb6033986a8fa5bcf65bb81c73e2b09.webm?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/4cb6033986a8fa5bcf65bb81c73e2b09.mp4?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造你的團隊</strong> <br>從四人小隊起步，隨著遊戲程序逐步擴大陣容。每名成員都擁有獨特的技能組合與個人風格。混合搭配不同職業、特技與飾品，為每項任務打造完美配置。 <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/ba1ceea25e20b629d7760a98e2174606.poster.avif?t=1770155301\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/ba1ceea25e20b629d7760a98e2174606.webm?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226830/extras/ba1ceea25e20b629d7760a98e2174606.mp4?t=1770155301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><strong>遊戲特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>原創故事與世界觀</strong>：在一個充滿敵對幫派、神秘人物與成長角色的戰役中，揭開塗鴉之城文化鎮壓背後的真相。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>掌握超過80種獨特技能與特技</strong>：為你的團隊配備種類繁多的戰鬥能力，包括增益、減益、區域控制、機動特技等等。每名角色都能帶來獨特的貢獻。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>招募與定製你的團隊</strong>：在戰役中解鎖12位可招募角色。每名角色都擁有獨特的風格、背景故事和能力選擇，可根據你的玩法進行塑造。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完成額外目標並建造車庫</strong>：達成支線目標可賺取稀有升級部件、解鎖新物品並充實你的車庫，車庫是你進行裝備配置、瞭解背景故事及制定任務計劃的大本營。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重玩任務以衝擊排名</strong>：重新挑戰已完成的關卡，最佳化你的策略，從而使得分最大化，並在每個關卡爭取最高排名。<strong></strong><br></p></li></ul>",
